              label.modal-content__label(for="user-name-field") Ваш e-mail:
              input.modal-content__input(type="text" name="user-email" id="user-email-field" placeholder="Для отправки ответа" maxlength="30")
          label.modal-content__label(for="email-text-field") Текст письма:
          textarea.modal-content__input.modal-content__input_email-text(rows="10" cols="45" name="email-text" id="email-text-field" placeholder="В свободной форме" maxlength="300")
        div.modal-content__btn-block
          button.btn.btn_red.btn_big(type="submit") Отправить
